oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: TVA Forest Nursery at Clinton, Tenn. "TVA Forest Nurseries have produced more than 420 million seedlings since 1934. About 80 percent of these seedlings were made available to 45,000 landowners through state forestry and agricultural extension agencies.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The other 20 percent were produced on contract for various public forestry agencies. The area reforested in the Tennessee Valley now stand at about 40,000 acres."
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Aerial views; Forestry; Nurseries (Horticulture)
